      "explanation": "H_GV^{(n_max)} = Sym(V) is the polynomial algebra on dim V = 15 primitive generators. Characters chi: H_GV -> Q (algebra maps with chi(1) = 1) are determined by their values on the dim V generators, giving Hom_alg(H_GV, Q) = V^* ~= Q^{dim V}. The group structure via convolution (chi*chi')(x_g) = chi(x_g) + chi'(x_g) on primitives makes this the additive group G_a^{dim V}."
